https://twitter.com/#!/shitmydadsays\" target=\"_blank\">shit their dads say</a> then why wouldn’t you be successful blogging about your dog…</p>\n<p>Anyway, maybe doing a little research is a better idea after all, hence this post. To find out what I’m on about feel free to check out <strong>my guest post at YoungPrePro</strong>.<span id=\"more-969\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/12-niche-searching-ideas\" target=\"_blank\">12 Audacious and Creative Niche Searching Ideas for Your Blog</a></p>\n<p>Once you have your niche there are still some things yet to do. For example, you have to decide <a href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/which-one-of-these-3-types-of-domain-names-is-the-best-one-for-you/\">which domain is right for you</a>, you have to find a WordPress theme (remember, <a href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/free-wordpress-themes-are-evil/\">free WordPress themes are evil</a>), and last but certainly not least – you have to find some <a href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/9200000-traffic-sources/\">blog traffic sources</a>.</p>\n\n\n<b>Related Posts</b>:\n<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/create-a-fake-niche/\">Can&#8217;t Find a Niche? Create a Fake One!</a><!-- (5.2)--></li>\n		<li><a href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/premature-publication/\">Don’t Commit the Premature Publication Sin, Ask Yourself These 9 Questions First</a><!-- (5)--></li>\n		<li><a href=\"http://newinternetorder.com/regret-i-didnt-come-up-with-these-myself-march-2011/\">Regret I Didn’t Come Up with These Myself… March 2011</a><!-- (4)--></li>\n	</ul>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/nio/~4/F8QTTvc4kZQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"xmlns\";a:8:{s:7:\"content\";s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";s:3:\"wfw\";s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";s:2:\"dc\";s:32:\"