lict causing the wp-admin screen to be blank (white screen error).</p>\n<p>It would appear the conflict is between W3TC and John Godley\'s Redirection plugin - anyone seen this before and any pointers for fixing it.</p>\n<p>I\'ve tried the suggested deactivate all plugins, and activate W3TC first and all goes well until I activate Redirection, likewise Redirection works fine without W3TC. Also tried putting the Wordpress code in the .htaccess file above the W3TC code as have seen this causing problems in the past.</p>\n<p>Any thoughts?</p>\n<p><strong>PS: Both great plugins by the way!!!</strong>\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/ooOMyeDZXCM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"http://wordpress.org/support/topic/wp-admin-white-screen-w3tc-and-redirection-conflict#post-1745156\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"johnnyone on \"PHP changes not updating instantly\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:115:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/XCVid3yo5MA/plugin-w3-total-cache-php-changes-not-updating-instantly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Mon, 18 Oct 2010 08:09:29 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;