y not.</p>\n<p>So after watching that video I have my General Settings set like this:</p>\n<p>General: unchecked<br />\nPage Cache: enable is checked, disk (enhanced)<br />\nMinify: enable is checked, disk<br />\nDatabase Cache: unchecked<br />\nObject Cache: enable is checked, disk<br />\nContent Delivery Network: unchecked<br />\nBrowser Cache: enable is checked</p>\n<p>I wish these plugins came with walkthru vids for dipshits like me.\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/KX6YkBqq8yw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:133:\"http://wordpress.org/support/topic/plugin-w3-total-cache-how-to-configure-w3-total-cache-to-optimize-website-performance#post-1743648\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:20;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"Umar Rasul on \"How to Configure w3 Total cache to Optimize website Performance\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:144:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/QIDpmO0rJLw/plugin-w3-total-cache-how-to-configure-w3-total-cache-to-optimize-website-performance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Sun, 17 Oct 2010 05:30:29 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"1743374@http://wordpress.org/support/\";s: