pdates, and develops websites.</p>\r\n<h3>Web Development...</h3>\r\n<p><img width=\"138\" height=\"94\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-664\" title=\"cogs\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/cos3.png\" />By website development we mean working with, or creating, an \'engine\' which drives dynamic websites. The pre-packaged versions of these are commonly known as Content Management Systems, and can allow website owners to edit content, list and sell products, create an image gallery, run a subscription service, and more. We also produce our own simple purpose-built \'engines\'.</p>\r\n<h3>Web Design...</h3>\r\n<p><img width=\"138\" height=\"96\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-400\" title=\"draughting table\" alt=\"draughting table\" src=\"http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/table4.gif\" />We\'re not from the design school which packs in gizmos and whirling things just because we can.</p>\r\n<p>We prefer to see and build web sites that are well-designed, yet clean, and fast-loading.&nbsp; In other words, sites which are built for end users - simple enough to understand, navigate and enjoy, but designed well enough for those users to enjoy. We like to think this site, and most of those in our <a title=\"View Our Portfolio\" href=\"/portfolio/\">portfolio</a>, meet those standards.</p>\r\n<h3>Hire us because...</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>We\'re <strong>affordable</strong>. Many small-to-medium sized businesses, or clubs, don\'t have bottomless pockets. We\'ll give you a quote, not a fright, and stick to that figure.</li>\r\n    <li>We build <strong>web sites</strong> which <strong>load fast</strong>, and display reliably across a range of platforms and operating systems, thanks to the use of modern methods of coding to <dfn title=\"eXtensible Mark-up Language\">XHTML</dfn> and <dfn title=\"Cascading Style Sheets\">CSS standards</dfn>.</li>\r\n    <li>We build sites which <strong>look good.</strong></li>\r\n    <li>Your site will be <strong>noticed</strong>. Our coding methods, and search engine knowledge give your website the best chance of being prominent in the relevant search engine results.&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>We focus on what\'s important to you. For example, do you want your site to achieve a financial target, are you focussed on attracting new customers, or do you have a readership target you want to meet?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To get started,&nbsp; <a title=\"go to our contact page\" href=\"/contact/\">contact us</a> now for a free, no-obligation quote for your website work.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','Home',0,'','publish','closed','open','','home','','','2011-06-26 23:30:47','2011-06-26 11:30:47','',0,'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0),(669,1,'2010-08-27 22:33:34','2010-08-27 10:33:34','<h3><a name=\"coding\">Website Coding</a></h3>\r\n<p>Urban Legend Web has for some years now worked on a contract basis for <a href=\"http://www.mcgovern.co.nz\">McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates</a>, a top Auckland web shop, and others. We\'re experts at cutting and coding websites using modern methods.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Content Management Systems</h3>\r\n<p><img width=\"138\" height=\"96\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-414\" alt=\"wordpress\" title=\"wordpress\" src=\"http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/wordpress2.gif\" />We can add one of these beasts, which allow a website owner - with little or no technical knowledge - to edit and update content and photographs.</p>\r\n<p>We work with Wordpress, Joomla, Drupal, and others.</p>\r\n<h3>Search Engine Optimisation</h3>\r\n<p>Have you got a website which is sitting there idle, unknown to the rest of the world?&nbsp;It may be fully functional in all other aspects, but unless it attracts visitors, you may as well not have bothered. We can help in using legitimate methods to drive more search engine traffic to your website.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Code Overhauls</h3>\r\n<p>Your website broken in browser x or y?&nbsp;Loading too slowly?&nbsp;The web is littered with sites coded using out-dated methods. These websites can be stream-lined to load more quickly, display more reliably, and be more easily updated.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Face-lifts</h3>\r\n<p>Do you have a site which looks like it was designed in the previous millenium?&nbsp; Perhaps it was. They say content is king, but visitors are much less likely to explore a web-site which is unattractively designed.</p>\r\n<h3>New Sites&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>We offer a range of services, from simple cookie-cutter brochure-type static web sites to&nbsp; custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce sites.</p>\r\n<p>We also do website code over-hauls, face-lifts, can add content management systems to allow website owners to edit content, and we can speed up your site.</p>\r\n<p>For new sites, we\'d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that\'s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>Below are some starting points, but you can always <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact/\">contact us</a>, tell us what you want, and we\'ll send you an obligation-free quote for your new website.</p>\r\n<h3>From $150</h3>\r\n<p>For businesses, clubs, and individuals wanting to make a first entrance on the web stage:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Brochure-type website</li>\r\n    <li>Bare-bones minimalist but functional design including your logo</li>\r\n    <li>Up to 3 pages including a contact page</li>\r\n    <li>Updates are charged by Urban Legend Web at reasonable rates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>From $600 </h3>\r\n<p>Custom-designed websites including an editable gallery / portfolio /&nbsp; products page, contact page, and the ability to update your site at will !</p>\r\n<p>Listed at <a target=\"newone\" title=\"Web Design Pros - opens in new window\" href=\"http://webdesignpros.co.nz/\">Web Design Pros</a></p>','Services',0,'','inherit','open','open','','90-revision-26','','','2010-08-27 22:33:34