ackaged versions of these are commonly known as Content Management Systems, and can allow website owners to edit content, list and sell products, create an image gallery, run a subscription service, and more. We also produce our own simple purpose-built \'engines\'.</p>\r\n<h3>Web Design...</h3>\r\n<p>We\'re not from the design school which packs in gizmos and whirling things just because we can.</p>\r\n<p>We like web sites that are well-designed, yet clean, and fast-loading.&nbsp; In other words, sites which are built for end users - simple enough to understand, navigate and enjoy, but designed well enough for those users to enjoy.</p>\r\n<p>We like to think this site, and most of those in our <a title=\"View Our Portfolio\" href=\"/portfolio/\">portfolio</a>, meet those standards.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Simpler Websites...</h3>\r\n<p>If on the other hand you need a simple brochure-type site, which doesn\'t change often, and is used mostly as a contact point for customers, club members, friends, or readers, we do these too.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>We\'re worth hiring because...</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>We\'re <strong>affordable</strong>. Many small-to-medium sized businesses, or clubs, don\'t have bottomless pockets. We\'ll give you a quote, not a fright, and stick to that figure.</li>\r\n    <li>We build <strong>web sites</strong> which <strong>load fast</strong>, and display reliably across a range of platforms and operating systems, thanks to the use of modern methods of coding to <def title=\"eXtensible Mark-up Language\">XHTML</def> and <def title=\"Cascading Style Sheets\">CSS standards</def>.</li>\r\n    <li>We build sites which <strong>look good.</strong></li>\r\n    <li>Your site will be <strong>noticed</strong>. Our coding methods, and search engine knowledge give your website the best chance of being prominent in the relevant search engine results.&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>We focus on what\'s important to you. For example, do you want your site to achieve a financial target, are you focussed on attracting new customers, or do you have a readership target you want to meet?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To get started,&nbsp; <a title=\"go to our contact page\" href=\"/contact/\">contact us</a> now for a free, no-obligation quote for your website work.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','Home',0,'','inherit','open','open','','18-revision-29','','','2010-05-20 00:27:40','2010-05-20 00:27:40','',18,'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/05/18-revision-29/',0,'revision','',0),(307,1,'2010-02-27 07:17:21','2010-02-27 07:17:21','<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop, run by Duncan O\'Neill,&nbsp; in Whangarei, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>We - including hired help when necessary -&nbsp; specialise in building websites for small to medium-sized businesses, and in contract website coding.</p>\r\n<p><img width=\"80\" height=\"122\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-254\" title=\"Duncan O\'Neill\" alt=\"me\" src=\"http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/me.gif\" />Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to update, it will be given its best chance to do well with search engines.</p>\r\n<p>We\'re well versed in most of the necessary Acronyms, and know our way around a handful of content management systems, such as&nbsp; <a href=\"http://wordpress.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Go to Wordpress\' site\">Wordpress</a>, <a href=\"http://www.oscommerce.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Go to osCommerce\'s site\">osCommerce</a>, <a href=\"http://www.joomla.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Goto Joomla\'s site\">Joomla</a>, and proprietary in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we update, overhaul, and code them for other people.</p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with <a href=\"http://www.easi.net.nz\" target=\"newone\" title=\"visit Easinet\'s site - opens in new window\">Easine