ouse commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we update, overhaul, and code them for other people.</p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with <a title=\"visit Easinet\'s site - opens in new window\" target=\"newone\" href=\"http://www.easi.net.nz\">Easinet</a> for hosting and other support.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"go to our contact page\" href=\"/contact/\">Contact us</a> for a&nbsp; quote.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','About',0,'','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-18','','','2010-05-27 15:34:56','2010-05-27 03:34:56','',2,'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/05/2-revision-18/',0,'revision','',0),(604,1,'2011-04-20 21:00:33','2011-04-20 09:00:33','<p>Some recent contract work just completed, via <a href=\"http://immersionmedia.com/\" target=\"newone\" title=\"visit Immersion Media - opens in new window\">Immersion Media</a>, a California company;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><a href=\"http://valueinvestingcongress.com/\" target=\"newone\" title=\"visit Value Investing Congress - opens in new window\">Value Investing Congress</a> ; I updated the jQuery behind the front-page slider to increase the delay for some slides</li>\r\n    <li><a href=\"http://valueinvestingletter.com\" target=\"newone\" title=\"visite Value Investing Letter - opens in new window\">Value Investing Letter</a>; I updated the <a title=\"opens in new window\" target=\"newone\" href=\"http://valueinvestingletter.com/value-investing-letter-video.html\">video landing page</a> by editing some <acronym title=\"php.net\">PHP</acronym> files behind the <a title=\"the modx content management system - opens in new window\" target=\"newone\" href=\"http://modx.com/\">modx</a> content management system which drives the site, and some <acronym title=\"cascading Style Sheets\">CSS</acronym> files for styling.</li>\r\n    <li>On the same site, we wrote code to protect privileged <a title=\"opens in new window\" target=\"newone\" href=\"http://valueinvestingletter.com/pdfs/Why_We_Covered_Our_Netflix_Short_T2%20P