ullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"390\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/Q3JToii4Aq4?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object></p>\n<p>Nuclear Weapons</p>\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"390\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/N-lADZG6-PI?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" /><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"390\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/N-lADZG6-PI?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object></p>\n<p>Of course, these three channels don’t have a monopoly for great visualizations, and there’s a lot more stuff out there. For example, these:</p>\n<p>History of the Internet</p>\n<p><object width=\"560\" height=\"349\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/9hIQjrMHTv4?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" /><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"560\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/9hIQjrMHTv4?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object></p>\n<p>The Animated Guide to Polish Success</p>\n<p><object width=\"560\" height=\"349\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/JC4xh1bO7ww?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" /><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"560\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/JC4xh1bO7ww?fs=1&amp;rel=0\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object></p>\n<p>Imagining the Tenth Dimension</p>\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"390\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/Jkxi